tagline.en: A team dedicated to the development and application of EOS.IO in China.
tagline.zh: 一个致力于EOS在中国发展和应用落地的团队.

introduce.en: A team dedicated to the development and application of EOS.IO in China.We will always remain independent, and contribute to the community in a continuous manner. We welcome oversight and inspection from everyone.
introduce.zh: EOSTEA是一个由社区驱动且保持中立的团队, 目前运营着最大的EOS开发者社区: eosfans.io
